Description: MokaPlayer
        ==========
        
        A simple music player written in python
        
        Features
        --------
        
        -  Support all the most popular music file formats
        -  Gapless playback
        -  Resumes playback on startup
        -  Automatically fetch:
        
           -  Album covers
           -  Lyrics
           -  ASCII and Guitar Pro tabs
        
